Problem Statement: Given a matrix if an element in the matrix is 0 then you will have to set its entire column and row to 0 and then return the matrix. It is also given that  the matrix contains only two element 0 and 1.
Example:
Input:  matrix=[[1,1,1],[1,0,1],[1,1,1]]
Output:  [[1,0,1],[0,0,0],[1,0,1]]